latestPosts.caption:
Our mission is to make the absolute best activewear for the people we love! Inspired by our cousins, our forever playmates, this line is for the many more outdoor play-times yet to come! 

#india#indians#indianfashion#playing#clothing#reels#indiatrends#indianreels#fun#happiness#mumbai#indianostalgia#nostalgic#reelsinstagram#indiangirls#bringingnoatalia#indianaesthetic#indiaaesthetics#mumbaidiaries#mumbaiaesthetic#activewear#indianactivewear#trendingreels#play#chasingendorphins

Starting with pure love for innovation & product and no fancy revenue numbers or targets. Work becomes all about numbers & metrics just so quick. Till you realise its all you real people we’re delivering too🥹💖. If you told me even just a few months ago, I’d be sending out over 200parcels daily to you guys, I wouldn’t believe you! Happiest to be the youngest founder at the fireside family🥺Pinching myself & so excited for adventure ahead! 🚀

latestPosts.caption:
Mom taught me to always cross the finish line first while dad taught me to work hard and think technically. And Dada always said: if something needs to be done, do it now, never later.
Im so grateful to realise, maybe those lessons did shape me. 👀
Still pinching myself and counting every blessing. I get to build my dream with my bestfriend! 

@rahee.07, we made it to Forbes Asia 30 Under 30!🥹🥹💖💖
#forbesu30asia
